Ladies and Gentlemen
I am the highly experienced Personal Assistant and I will be happy to have an opportunity to prove this by our work for you.
I have a lot of experience working for VIP clients (for example as Personal and Travel Assistant for family of known Deputy of Russian Parliament). I  have many  years experience of working as  housekeeper and  personal  assistant  also on  the  board of luxury yacht as stewardess. I can see the details and give them a lot of attention. No matter what was the object of  my  responsibility – a disabled person or  private villa,  the  housekeeping  on  the  yacht,  or assisting  by  travel,  sport, or  every day  life, - I was always able to set the aims correctly, to select the necessary resources economically, successfully reaching the goals in the scheduled time and with high quality of the result. 
I am able to provide so excellent results, because I myself can perform all jobs professionally with very high standards by my own hands. I have perfect experience not only in real estate management and as doctor medicine but also in cleaning and interior maintenance, including on the board of luxury yacht. Cooking is for me overall not a problem.
Despite of my age I have perfect health and I am very strong. My perfect  health  is proved by my yearly medical  attestation for  sea job,  and  as scuba dive leader  and  ski instructor.  Nevertheless if you doubt that I am appropriate worker for you, I am ready to prove my qualification and ability to satisfy your demands during the trial period, and if you say “NOT”, I will go away without any contribution. But I am sure that it will be not a case.
I speak fluent English, German, Russian; I speak French at a basic level.
I live in Stuttgart Germany and want to change for South of France now. I will obtain the EU citizenship in 2019. But if the job permission in France will be necessary immediately, I will obtain this permission very fast.
My CV you will find in attachment.
Interview is anytime possible via Skype  or viber
Let me know your e-mail address, I will send to you my reference and certificates. I hope to hear from you soon
Best regards 
Zhanna
