"05/28/2019 05:22am","109.133.113.37","0","22/05/1983","fadouamachboua@gmail.com","+32488405369","En couple","Secrétaire particulier","Assistante personnelle mi temps","Je suis qualifiée en administration depuis plus de 10ans. 
